WEBVTT

00:02:07.750 --> 00:02:09.210
[rice cooker beeping]

00:02:09.290 --> 00:02:10.510
[KOGUMA]
Hmm?

00:03:35.010 --> 00:03:38.180
[KOGUMA]
Hokuto, Yamanashi Prefecture.

00:03:38.260 --> 00:03:42.140
Downhill from Hinoharu Station
on the Chuo Main Line,

00:03:42.220 --> 00:03:46.100
past Koshu Highway is
a long, low incline.

00:03:46.180 --> 00:03:49.100
[panting]

00:03:49.190 --> 00:03:51.060
[KOGUMA]
I have no parents.

00:03:51.150 --> 00:03:52.650
No money.

00:03:52.730 --> 00:03:55.400
No hobbies or anything.

00:03:55.480 --> 00:03:57.490
Nobody to call a friend.

00:03:57.570 --> 00:03:59.780
No goals for my future.

00:04:06.250 --> 00:04:08.960
[KOGUMA]
Yes. I really am...

00:04:14.420 --> 00:04:21.430
[school bell chiming]

00:04:27.560 --> 00:04:29.850
[TEACHER 1A] I hope you've
all had a pleasant morning.

00:04:29.940 --> 00:04:32.270
Let's see... Any absences?

00:04:32.350 --> 00:04:34.310
There don't appear to be.

00:04:34.400 --> 00:04:35.730
Right, then!

00:04:36.860 --> 00:04:40.280
[REIKO] "They knew that
they could go anywhere

00:04:40.360 --> 00:04:42.120
with the motorcycle.

00:04:42.200 --> 00:04:45.200
That's why they could
say most happily

00:04:45.280 --> 00:04:46.830
where they would go tomorrow."

00:04:46.910 --> 00:04:48.830
Hey, were watching
the show last night?

00:04:48.910 --> 00:04:50.620
Man, you couldn't believe it―

00:04:57.800 --> 00:04:59.920
So, like, I was scrolling
through videos on the Internet

00:05:00.010 --> 00:05:01.300
'cause that's
basically all I do,

00:05:01.380 --> 00:05:04.180
and I'm, like, obsessed
with this one girl I found!

00:05:04.260 --> 00:05:05.890
She lives up in Hokkaido,
and she―

00:05:12.640 --> 00:05:17.690
[school bell chiming]

00:05:24.530 --> 00:05:28.950
[STUDENTS murmuring]

00:05:37.250 --> 00:05:38.380
[sighs]

00:05:56.560 --> 00:05:58.020
[KOGUMA grunts]

00:06:02.860 --> 00:06:09.580
[KOGUMA panting]

00:06:15.040 --> 00:06:17.840
[panting continues]

00:06:17.920 --> 00:06:19.210
Huh?

00:06:32.680 --> 00:06:33.730
[KOGUMA]
Ah?

00:06:37.440 --> 00:06:39.150
Too much...

00:06:48.580 --> 00:06:50.530
Looking to buy a scooter?

00:06:53.120 --> 00:06:55.540
Well, I've been thinking
about getting one lately.

00:06:55.620 --> 00:06:57.290
But it looks like everything
here is way more

00:06:57.380 --> 00:06:58.840
than I can afford.

00:06:58.920 --> 00:07:01.500
[SHINO] Huh. Have you
thought of buying used?

00:07:03.260 --> 00:07:04.970
[KOGUMA]
Mm?

00:07:05.880 --> 00:07:07.220
Uh...

00:07:25.530 --> 00:07:26.700
[SHINO grunts]

00:07:37.710 --> 00:07:40.750
[KOGUMA]
Um... I'm really broke.

00:07:42.000 --> 00:07:43.630
[SHINO]
Just 10,000 yen.

00:07:43.710 --> 00:07:45.010
[KOGUMA]
Uh...?

00:07:46.760 --> 00:07:48.260
Mm...

00:07:58.900 --> 00:08:00.440
[gasps]

00:08:08.110 --> 00:08:09.610
[gasps]

00:08:12.830 --> 00:08:14.870
Yeah. I'll take it.

00:08:16.160 --> 00:08:17.500
[SHINO sighs]

00:08:19.330 --> 00:08:22.000
But why is the price so low?

00:08:22.090 --> 00:08:24.750
[SHINO grunts]

00:08:24.840 --> 00:08:28.470
This bike... has some history.

00:08:28.550 --> 00:08:30.010
Three deaths.

00:08:30.090 --> 00:08:31.010
And that's all?

00:08:31.090 --> 00:08:32.800
Huh?

00:08:32.890 --> 00:08:34.390
I'll take it.

00:08:35.930 --> 00:08:38.310
[SHINO]
Hmm.

00:08:38.390 --> 00:08:39.980
Follow me.

00:08:42.400 --> 00:08:46.280
[SHINO] Name goes there, and you
can fill out your address here.

00:08:55.120 --> 00:08:58.200
Won't I... need a license?

00:08:58.290 --> 00:08:59.830
[SHINO]
Hmm...

00:09:05.500 --> 00:09:09.670
[SHINO] The questions on
the test never seem to change.

00:09:33.070 --> 00:09:34.280
[sighs]

00:09:43.830 --> 00:09:45.210
[SHINO]
Hmm?

00:09:52.970 --> 00:09:54.590
[KOGUMA]
Mm...

00:09:59.640 --> 00:10:01.770
Uh. Thank you so much, sir.

00:10:01.850 --> 00:10:03.940
You've got a helmet
and gloves, yes?

00:10:04.020 --> 00:10:06.150
I have them here in my bag.

00:10:10.610 --> 00:10:14.110
[SHINO]
Hmm. Hold on just a moment.

00:10:23.330 --> 00:10:25.250
[SHINO]
You should take these.

00:10:29.800 --> 00:10:32.590
Have they been involved
in any fatal accidents?

00:10:32.670 --> 00:10:35.010
[SHINO]
Hmph. They're new.

00:10:36.680 --> 00:10:38.800
[SHINO]
It's a promotional deal.

00:10:45.270 --> 00:10:47.100
[SHINO] You should bring
it back for an oil change

00:10:47.190 --> 00:10:49.690
once you've ridden
100 kilometers.

00:10:49.770 --> 00:10:52.400
That's especially important
for keeping the engine in shape

00:10:52.480 --> 00:10:54.360
on a used one like this.

00:10:54.450 --> 00:10:55.740
Okay.

00:10:55.820 --> 00:10:58.450
[SHINO] And I'll
leave this right in here.

00:11:05.290 --> 00:11:06.580
[SHINO grunts]

00:11:12.300 --> 00:11:14.760
First, you wanna release
the handlebar lock,

00:11:14.840 --> 00:11:18.720
turn the key to "on," then just
give the pedal a good kick.

00:11:18.800 --> 00:11:20.350
I think I get it.

00:11:22.350 --> 00:11:23.730
[sighs]

00:11:36.360 --> 00:11:37.700
[KOGUMA]
Mm?

00:11:47.120 --> 00:11:50.380
Gonna need to
give it a harder kick.

00:11:50.460 --> 00:11:52.170
[KOGUMA whimpers]

00:11:59.260 --> 00:12:02.430
It might be easier, knowing
the basics of how it works.

00:12:02.510 --> 00:12:04.430
Wanna give it another go?

00:12:06.100 --> 00:12:08.020
So before I kick...

00:12:08.100 --> 00:12:11.610
...I should gradually move
the pedal with my foot...

00:12:11.690 --> 00:12:14.730
...and find the position
where I feel it pushing back.

00:12:16.400 --> 00:12:17.320
[KOGUMA gasps]

00:12:17.400 --> 00:12:18.910
[engine puttering]

00:12:24.040 --> 00:12:25.870
[KOGUMA]
Then, put it in gear.

00:12:29.790 --> 00:12:31.210
[gasps]

00:12:39.760 --> 00:12:41.890
[KOGUMA] Thanks so much
for your help, sir!

00:12:47.560 --> 00:12:48.940
[SHINO sighs]

00:12:54.900 --> 00:12:56.690
Ah?

00:12:58.610 --> 00:12:59.820
Hmm.

00:13:22.510 --> 00:13:23.930
[gasps]

00:13:26.180 --> 00:13:27.350
[KOGUMA whimpers]

00:13:47.240 --> 00:13:48.540
[sighs]

00:14:35.580 --> 00:14:36.750
[sighs]

00:14:45.550 --> 00:14:46.800
[KOGUMA]
Hmm...

00:14:48.720 --> 00:14:49.890
Uh?

00:15:02.320 --> 00:15:05.530
[sighs]
I need a chain lock...

00:15:05.610 --> 00:15:07.820
Meaning a trip to
the hardware store.

00:15:09.240 --> 00:15:10.910
[KOGUMA]
Oh, right!

00:15:10.990 --> 00:15:12.540
On my Cub!

00:15:17.000 --> 00:15:18.340
[gasps]

00:15:33.390 --> 00:15:34.480
[ding]

00:15:53.200 --> 00:15:54.620
[sighs]

00:16:10.470 --> 00:16:11.640
[KOGUMA]
Mm...?

00:16:12.720 --> 00:16:13.970
Hmm.

00:16:22.570 --> 00:16:23.820
[KOGUMA grunts]

00:16:37.330 --> 00:16:38.710
[KOGUMA] I should probably
hurry up and learn

00:16:38.790 --> 00:16:40.750
to ride it properly.

00:17:10.070 --> 00:17:11.870
Ah?

00:17:11.950 --> 00:17:13.070
Hmm.

00:17:27.000 --> 00:17:29.630
[KOGUMA groans]

00:17:35.550 --> 00:17:37.770
[KOGUMA] The convenience
store at night...

00:17:39.390 --> 00:17:40.690
Stay cool.

00:17:53.870 --> 00:17:55.450
[chuckles]

00:18:04.080 --> 00:18:05.290
[KOGUMA]
Ah?

00:18:07.290 --> 00:18:09.670
Before kicking the pedal,
I need to move it back and forth

00:18:09.760 --> 00:18:11.340
gently with my foot,

00:18:11.420 --> 00:18:14.800
until I find the point where
I can feel it pushing back.

00:18:16.470 --> 00:18:17.810
Huh...?

00:18:27.980 --> 00:18:29.530
[KOGUMA]
What's wrong...?

00:18:43.830 --> 00:18:44.750
[MAN 1A]
You okay?

00:18:44.830 --> 00:18:46.000
[KOGUMA]
Ah?

00:18:46.080 --> 00:18:48.460
It looks like you've got
something bothering ya.

00:18:48.550 --> 00:18:50.670
Oh. I'm fine, thanks.

00:18:50.760 --> 00:18:53.510
[MAN 1A] Hmm. Well,
it's getting late, so be careful

00:18:53.590 --> 00:18:55.340
on your way back home.

00:18:55.430 --> 00:18:57.010
Right, sure.

00:18:58.390 --> 00:18:59.680
[coins clattering]

00:18:59.760 --> 00:19:02.310
[MAN 1A]
Aw, for friggin'―

00:19:02.390 --> 00:19:06.190
[growls]
Hate having to carry change...

00:19:08.060 --> 00:19:09.440
[gasps]

00:19:13.030 --> 00:19:15.450
[SHINO] And I'll leave
this right in here.

00:19:16.990 --> 00:19:18.740
[KOGUMA]
Mm...

00:19:21.790 --> 00:19:23.080
[gasps]

00:19:27.620 --> 00:19:32.380
[KOGUMA] "When the engine
won't turn over." On page 89!

00:19:34.380 --> 00:19:35.720
[gasps]

00:19:39.550 --> 00:19:41.220
[KOGUMA]
The gas tank...?

00:19:47.900 --> 00:19:49.270
[KOGUMA]
Ah?

00:19:52.320 --> 00:19:53.570
Ah?

00:19:53.650 --> 00:19:55.820
The fuel petcock.

00:19:55.900 --> 00:19:59.910
"R-E-S." Reserve fuel!

00:20:12.670 --> 00:20:14.300
[sighs]

00:20:24.970 --> 00:20:26.520
[whimpers softly]

00:20:32.900 --> 00:20:34.530
[KOGUMA]
Mm!

00:20:34.610 --> 00:20:36.950
[engine revvs]

00:20:41.530 --> 00:20:46.830
[KOGUMA panting]

00:20:59.680 --> 00:21:03.010
[KOGUMA] "Unscrew the gas
cap from the fuel inlet.

00:21:03.100 --> 00:21:05.760
Fill the tank with gasoline
until the fuel is even with

00:21:05.850 --> 00:21:09.350
the lower edge of
the filler neck." Got it.

00:21:26.160 --> 00:21:27.790
[KOGUMA sighs]

00:21:29.460 --> 00:21:31.210
I'm finally home...

00:21:31.290 --> 00:21:32.960
That could've been so bad...

00:21:33.040 --> 00:21:38.010
[panting]

00:21:40.170 --> 00:21:46.640
[alarm beeping]

00:21:46.720 --> 00:21:47.970
[KOGUMA]
Mm?

00:23:14.390 --> 00:23:15.600
[KOGUMA]
Good.

00:23:19.070 --> 00:23:21.440
"Warm up the engine.

00:23:21.530 --> 00:23:22.780
But not too long."

00:23:22.860 --> 00:23:24.200
Okay.

00:23:28.370 --> 00:23:31.540
So... is that enough?

00:23:37.000 --> 00:23:40.750
[KOGUMA] A full tank
is just over 500 yen.

00:23:40.840 --> 00:23:42.510
On the Chuo Main Line,

00:23:42.590 --> 00:23:44.970
that would get me
to around Kofu.

00:23:47.930 --> 00:23:49.680
[KOGUMA]
Until yesterday...

00:23:49.760 --> 00:23:51.390
...I didn't have anything.

00:23:52.770 --> 00:23:57.600
But... from now on,
I have my Cub.

00:24:02.610 --> 00:24:06.030
[KOGUMA]
I wonder, how far will we go?

00:24:17.210 --> 00:24:19.540
[KOGUMA] Episode 2,
"Reiko."